Confirmed ~ That means it said that they found violations

Duplicate ~ That means they had calls already from that location

Site Not Available ~ That means they went to check on the request and were not able to access the site or it had dangerous conditions and they did not look

No Evidence ~ That means they went, did not see evidence of rats

Minor Violations ~ That means it passed but had minor violations

Owner is Fixing ~ Owner has been provided with information on how to fix or has been told they need to fix it

Incorrect Address ~ That means they could not identify the address on the report

Referred to Another Agency ~ Report fell under another agency’s jurisdiction 

Took Action ~ The agency took action

In Progess ~ That means it is still open
